Glitterati, which is a component used in his products, contains carmine. Carmine is NOT cruelty-free nor vegan, it is a red pigment made from crushed insects. Also, using a cruelty-free logo on your products, when they're really not cruelty-free, is wrong!

Please address this issue, Brad...
